# hayabusa-plus: keep build/runtime assets that the broad *.txt / *.css rules
# above would otherwise drop. RustEmbed embeds art/ and config/ at COMPILE
# time, so a clone without these fails to build (#[folder="art/"] missing).
!art/
!art/*.txt
!config/*.txt
!config/html_report/*.css
